{"tid":1781444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天有異象？英國300隻鳥「一起死」　活活摔地臟器到處噴","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:37:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53cb9802be56f01ced60e218ed4ac79feb0c9f37","tid":1781444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=653131&amp;p=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D653131%26p%3D0&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6gfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=a69e1772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D653131%26p%3D0&h=fbc63f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=653131&amp;p=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/13/2299449-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F2299449-XXL.jpg&h=7952ec95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n每當發生無法解釋的事件，總會聽到有人說「天有異象」，人心惶惶地認為，可能將有不祥的大事發生。日前，英國有對情侶拍下300隻鳥集體死亡的恐怖景象，詭異的是，這些會飛的鳥竟都是「摔死的」，路上布滿鳥屍，且內臟四處噴濺，樹枝上也掛有垂死掙扎的鳥群，看起來怵目驚心，讓人不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/13/2299447-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F2299447-XXL.jpg&h=90633f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼▲英國一對情侶拍下數百隻鳥集體死亡的詭異畫面。（圖／翻攝自Youtube）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/13/2299446-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F13%2F2299446-XXL.jpg&h=0bc673e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，日前，英國一對情侶在安格爾西島（Isle of Anglesey）拍下超過300隻鳥集體死亡的畫面， 讓人不解的是，這些會飛的鳥竟都是摔死的，鳥屍布滿公路上，看起來氣氛相當詭異。<br />\n<br />\n據住在安格爾西島的女子漢娜（Hannah Stevens）說，事發當時，她恰好看到一群鳥從頭頂飛過，飛行途中鳥群嘴裡好像有在進食，約莫過了1個小時，當漢娜再次經過當初看到鳥群的地點時，發現公路上竟布滿摔死的鳥屍，內臟還四處噴濺，慘不忍睹，這一幕讓漢娜嚇壞，簡直不敢相信自己的眼睛，立刻告訴男友達菲德（Dafydd Edward）。<br />\n<br />\n接到通知的達菲德起初還不相信，直到他親自抵達現場，看到地上的鳥屍、掛在樹上垂死的鳥群，頓時讓他汗毛直豎、背脊發涼，不明白這裡到底發生什麼事，據達菲德說，他曾經試圖要數有多少鳥屍，但數量實在太多，他算到150隻就放棄，達菲德肯定地說，絕對超過3百隻，相當可怖。據媒體報導，目前這些鳥群的死因還有待釐清，不排除是吃到汙染的食物。（詹婷惠報導）<br />\n<br />\n鳥群離奇死亡影片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DIeWKqD9lWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDIeWKqD9lWQ&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6gfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=9b5deb3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DIeWKqD9lWQ</a>"},{"pid":"84e215666e9ac51ca0f62b8f2c263baaadeb77fa","tid":1781444,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"Pull"},{"pid":"4267e7effd5e3d28c128f0cf729cc532582f3ee3","tid":1781444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e215666e9ac51ca0f62b8f2c263baaadeb77fa","tid":1781444,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"Pull"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e5d40fba488dc4f064292db0b7e985b568fb59","tid":1781444,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:08:57.000Z","msg":"脫歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c19a0d15f0b226dd2c4fb20e380056f9c88c266","tid":1781444,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0102d0fdceec4c139dd5ca13a0d86f455c679488","tid":1781444,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e215666e9ac51ca0f62b8f2c263baaadeb77fa","tid":1781444,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"Pull"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"係時候上水喇"},{"pid":"77d57f839ebb5b8b014df6b235740aadbd9e3f9a","tid":1781444,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"DARK netflix"},{"pid":"a9635bff8a07d4a9d008473366291b88b3525d4d","tid":1781444,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4267e7effd5e3d28c128f0cf729cc532582f3ee3","tid":1781444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84e215666e9ac51ca0f62b8f2c263baaadeb77fa","tid":1781444,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"Pull"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"條友on9仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b988c94afaee036dec1a99fdca9b1facc12ab30b","tid":1781444,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"入lift啦我 潛左去邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老母報夢比我話佢好凍"},{"pid":"4931b409b3f00445e8158b30f7a2bed05fc57697","tid":1781444,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"聲波炮？"}]}